; TL 22.3 mm , SL 19.4 mm ; M. Machado leg.; MB (Accesion number: 11 - 000932).

Thorax fusiform, wider at 6 th or 7 th somite level. Eleventh thoracic somite with lateral lobes at the posterior 20– 25 % of its length. Dorsally, each thoracic somite carries one pair of warty outgrowths with a central sensilla, similarly to other anostracan species (
Linder, 1941
).
